On Today's Dan Patrick Show, DP recaps last night's Bucs/Bears Game. Are we seeing a different Tom Brady in Tampa? We're joined by Pro Football Talk Live's Mike Florio, Bears QB Nick Foles, and 7- time NBA Finals Champion Robert Horry.
